{"data":[{"date":"14:20 16/08","title":"C\u1ee9 v\u1eefng tin, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eeba s\u1ee9c h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Olympic Nepal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/cu-vung-tin-olympic-viet-nam-thua-suc-ha-guc-olympic-nepal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 tin tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Nepal l\u00fac 19h h\u00f4m nay. Nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam \u00c1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 \"r\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ef1ng b\u00f3ng\" t\u1ea1i ASIAD.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Nepal ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng n\u00e0o trong 5 k\u1ef3 ASIAD g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y h\u1ecd tham d\u1ef1. \u0110\u00e1ng n\u00f3i, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1982, tr\u1eadn Nepal thua Kuwait 1-3. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn nay, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam \u00c1 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn 65 b\u00e0n, ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c n\u00e0o &quot;r\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ef1ng b\u00f3ng&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, Nepal ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 0-1, tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 do \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 phung ph\u00ed qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7m c\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, song Olympic Nepal v\u1eabn m\u01a1 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia Nepal to\u00e0n thua Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i AFC Asian Cup 2003, v\u1edbi c\u00e1c t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-5 v\u00e0 0-2.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ee9 v\u1eefng tin, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eeba s\u1ee9c h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Olympic Nepal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ee9 v\u1eefng tin, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eeba s\u1ee9c h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Olympic Nepal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/6_Zing_21.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Nepal kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u1ea2nh: Zing.vn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng ng\u0103n tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Nepal ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u1ea3 quan. Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Bal Gopal Maharjan c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Nepal \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00f4m nay. N\u1ebfu ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo th\u1ec3 l\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i, hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed7i b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 b\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 ba c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out ASIAD. &quot;K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a s\u1ebd t\u0103ng th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Olympic Nepal. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u00ecm \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Vi\u1ec7t Nam&quot;, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Bal Gopal Maharjan cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng theo \u00f4ng n\u00e0y, tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Pakistan m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D. V\u00ec v\u1eady, m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a h\u00f4m nay s\u1ebd m\u1edf ra nhi\u1ec1u hy v\u1ecdng cho tuy\u1ec3n Nepal. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Olympic Nepal \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 b\u00ea t\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh nh\u01b0 t\u1eebng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam \u00c1 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, b\u1edfi th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 hai \u0111\u1ed9i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n qu\u00e1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&quot;V\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n thua. Nh\u01b0ng khi g\u1eb7p Pakistan, Nepal s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 theo c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c. L\u00fac \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i d\u1ed3n to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c cho m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng&quot;, \u00f4ng Bal Gopal Maharjan n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018, tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Nepal ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n 9 ng\u00e0y t\u1ea1i Bangkok (Th\u00e1i Lan), \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu 2 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p CLB Tero Police FC thu\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3i Thai League 1 v\u00e0 U23 Th\u00e1i Lan. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Nepal to\u00e0n thua v\u1edbi c\u00e1c t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 0-1 v\u00e0 0-4.<br>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-194598.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-nepal-truong-thanh-tu-hoc-vien-bong-da-tottenham-quyet-tam-xe-luoi-bui-tien-dung-168-194596.html\">Sao tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Tottenham '\u0111e d\u1ecda' Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cuu-hlv-truong-dt-viet-nam-nepal-khong-co-cua-so-voi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-168-194590.html\">C\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam: &ldquo;Nepal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda so v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang-168-194581.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal (19h ng\u00e0y 16/8): Duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/rohit-chand-cau-thu-nepal-ma-olympic-viet-nam-phai-de-chung-nhat-472-194579.html\">Rohit Chand, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nepal m\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng nh\u1ea5t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nepal-da-doi-cong-voi-olympic-viet-nam-168-194546.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n Nepal \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/u23-nepal-cung-co-thu-mon-quoc-dan-nhu-bui-tien-dung-472-194545.html\">U23 Nepal c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n nh\u01b0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2438","checkdouble":"194608"},{"date":"15:12 16/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nepal 19h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (Asiad 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nepal: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal b\u1ea3ng B m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018 l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 16/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nepal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ch\u00fang ta ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean BXH, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nepal xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nepal xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nX\u00e9t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, Nepal kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng s\u00e1nh vai c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ea7y kinh nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1eadn m\u1ea1c v\u00e0 v\u1eeba gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Olympic Nepal t\u1edbi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00edt t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1eb7ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam \u00c1 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ecd x\u00e1t, t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i Th\u1ec3 thao Nam \u00c1 \u1edf Bangladesh v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 3/2019.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018, Olympic Nepal v\u1eeba c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn thua tan t\u00e1c 0-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian qua l\u00e0 Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u1eafng c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iraq, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Kuwait v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 13 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2014. Nh\u1eefng d\u1eef li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2437","checkdouble":"194609"},{"date":"15:13 16/08","title":"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nepal th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/truyen-thong-nepal-thua-nhan-suc-manh-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ngo\u00e0i mong \u0111\u1ee3i, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Malaysia \u0111ang v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Chi\u1ec1u qua (15/8), Olympic Malaysia \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn khi th\u1eafng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Kyrgyzstan 3-1. Hi\u1ec7n sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Malaysia t\u1ea1m x\u1ebfp nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng sau H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c do k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i Kyrgyzstan, HLV Ong Kim Swee \u0111ang v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 tin khi cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn, HLV Olympic Malaysia l\u1edbn ti\u1ebfng d\u1ecda c\u1ea3 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"G\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn, HLV Olympic Malaysia l\u1edbn ti\u1ebfng d\u1ecda c\u1ea3 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/untitled-1534406334930473824037.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Malaysia \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ng\u00f4i sao Son Heung-min, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p Malaysia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Malaysia. H\u1ecd c\u00f2n l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf Asiad. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ebf m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi h\u1ecd. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 20 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0u k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Malaysia s\u1ebd g\u00e2y ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. Son Heung-min \u01b0? Trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n 1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc, 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Safawi Rasid, Akhyar Rashid v\u00e0 Syafiq Ahmad l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng khi ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Kyrgyzstan. Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y, Safawi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m: \"T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n \u0111ang gi\u00fap Malaysia t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kho\u1ea3ng v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, HLV Ong Kim Swee t\u1eebng r\u1ea5t bi quan v\u00e0 c\u00f2n tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i r\u00fat lui kh\u1ecfi Asiad do s\u1ee3 kh\u00f4ng gom \u0111\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean U23 Malaysia t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. C\u00f2n nh\u1edb h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 (gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1eadp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n), U23 Malaysia c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ong Kim Swee l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-nepal-la-doi-bong-3-te-tai-asiad-168-194611.html\">Olympic Nepal l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u201c3 t\u1ec7\u201d t\u1ea1i ASIAD</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-nepal-thua-nhan-suc-manh-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194610.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nepal th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/cu-vung-tin-olympic-viet-nam-thua-suc-ha-guc-olympic-nepal-472-194608.html\">C\u1ee9 v\u1eefng tin, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eeba s\u1ee9c h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Olympic Nepal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018-372-194609.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nepal 19h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (Asiad 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-nhat-ban-vs-u23-pakistan-asiad-2018-372-194605.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs U23 Pakistan 16h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (Asiad 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-thai-lan-vs-u23-bangladesh-asiad-2018-372-194604.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Th\u00e1i Lan vs U23 Bangladesh 16h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (Asiad 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-cu-tro-ly-do-tham-han-quoc-168-194601.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1eed tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd do th\u00e1m H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng H\u1ee3p (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2436","checkdouble":"194610"},{"date":"15:32 16/08","title":"Olympic Nepal l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u201c3 t\u1ec7\u201d t\u1ea1i ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/olympic-nepal-la-doi-bong-3-te-tai-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Nepal l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed ASIAD khi h\u1ecd \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu 3 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i n\u00e0y.</h2><div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018-372-194609.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018-372-194609.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nepal 19h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (Asiad 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nepal: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal b\u1ea3ng B m\u00f4n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nepal t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn nay kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao khi tham gia s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 161 tr\u00ean BXH FIFA.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD n\u0103m nay, Nepal \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-1. D\u1eabu sao \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t trong nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Nepal l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng 3 t\u1ec7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Olympic Nepal l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng 3 t\u1ec7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/Nhan-dinh-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Nepal,-(19h-ngay-168)-Duy-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Olympic Nepal t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea, Nepal to\u00e0n thua trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD. N\u0103m 1982, h\u1ecd thua 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng (ghi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 9 l\u1ea7n).\u00a0T\u1edbi k\u1ef3 ASIAD n\u0103m 1986, h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 4 tr\u1eadn \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng (0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 17 b\u00e0n thua). <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m 1994, Nepal ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u1ea1i thua 3 tr\u1eadn \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng (0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 20 b\u00e0n thua). \u0110\u00e1ng n\u00f3i h\u01a1n, tr\u1eadn thua 0-11 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c khi \u1ea5y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eadm nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed ASIAD t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 1998, Nepal l\u1ea1i thua 3 tr\u1eadn \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng (0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 5 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi). \u0110\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2002, h\u1ecd m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa l\u00e0m b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn 3 l\u1ea7n (0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 13 b\u00e0n thua).\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cho t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, qu\u1ed1c gia Nam \u00c1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 17 tr\u1eadn thua trong 17 tr\u1eadn tham d\u1ef1 \u1edf ASIAD. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 qu\u1ed1c gia duy nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a t\u1ea1i ASIAD. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nepal c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t ASIAD v\u1edbi 64 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi trong l\u1ecbch s\u1ef1 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi \u2018th\u00e0nh t\u00edch\u2019, kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u hi v\u1ecdng cho vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i nay 16/8.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-nepal-thua-nhan-suc-manh-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194610.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/truyen-thong-nepal-thua-nhan-suc-manh-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-nepal-thua-nhan-suc-manh-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194610.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nepal th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Nepal v\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c gia Nam \u00c1 Nepal cho r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-cu-tro-ly-do-tham-han-quoc-168-194601.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-cu-tro-ly-do-tham-han-quoc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-cu-tro-ly-do-tham-han-quoc-168-194601.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1eed tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd do th\u00e1m H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho hai tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd t\u1edbi xem, ghi h\u00ecnh tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 6-0 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain h\u00f4m qua 15/8.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-nepal-truong-thanh-tu-hoc-vien-bong-da-tottenham-quyet-tam-xe-luoi-bui-tien-dung-168-194596.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/sao-nepal-truong-thanh-tu-hoc-vien-bong-da-tottenham-quyet-tam-xe-luoi-bui-tien-dung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-nepal-truong-thanh-tu-hoc-vien-bong-da-tottenham-quyet-tam-xe-luoi-bui-tien-dung-168-194596.html\">Sao tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Tottenham \u0111e d\u1ecda Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nG\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110T Olympic Nepal \u0111ang t\u1ecf r\u00f5 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cuu-hlv-truong-dt-viet-nam-nepal-khong-co-cua-so-voi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-168-194590.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/cuu-hlv-truong-dt-viet-nam-nepal-khong-co-cua-so-voi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cuu-hlv-truong-dt-viet-nam-nepal-khong-co-cua-so-voi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-168-194590.html\">C\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam: \u201cNepal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda so v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo\u201d</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eafc n\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nam \u00c1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5 cho...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2435","checkdouble":"194611"},{"date":"16:43 16/08","title":"\"Mourinho v\u00e0 Pogba s\u1ebd t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/mourinho-va-pogba-se-tim-duoc-cach-giai-quyet-mau-thuan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Berbatov cho r\u1eb1ng HLV Mourinho v\u00e0 Pogba s\u1ebd t\u00ecm ra c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i Premier League \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1eabn c\u00f2n quy\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1edbi h\u1ebft th\u00e1ng 8. V\u00ec v\u1eady, Pogba v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Barca ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Dimitar Berbatov cho r\u1eb1ng Man United v\u1eabn d\u1ef1a kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a Pogba n\u00ean s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Berbatov c\u0169ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Pogba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Mourinho n\u1ebfu c\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho v\u00e0 Pogba s\u1ebd t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho v\u00e0 Pogba s\u1ebd t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/mourinho-va-pogba-se-tim-duoc-cach-giai-quyet-mau-thuan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Berbatov tin r\u1eb1ng Mourinho v\u00e0 Pogba s\u1ebd t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi th\u1ea5y m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Pogba tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester. \u0110\u00f3 qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng\u201d, Berbatov chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi trang betfair.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf kh\u1eafp m\u1ecdi n\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t, th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n qu\u1ea3 penalty ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin l\u1edbn. \u0110\u00f3 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u1ee3i khen.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTruy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 b\u00e1o \u0111\u00e0i lu\u00f4n t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00f3. H\u1ecd lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t cho b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai. Nh\u01b0ng Mourinho v\u00e0 Pogba s\u1ebd t\u00ecm ra c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nBerbatov c\u0169ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng HLV Jose Mourinho c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u1ed9i thu cho Man United d\u00f9 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111em l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cTu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Man United v\u00e0 Leicester s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t \u00edt \u1ecfi. V\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ec9 1 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMan United \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p may m\u1eafn cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn. Leicester c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u00ecn chung \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u00e1c C\u0110V Man United mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft. T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u s\u1ef1 gi\u1eadn d\u1eef c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd nh\u01b0ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n th\u1eafng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 1 b\u00e0n c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t th\u00ec b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i \u0111a\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2434","checkdouble":"194612"},{"date":"15:43 16/08","title":"G\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn, HLV Olympic Malaysia l\u1edbn ti\u1ebfng \u201cd\u1ecda\u201d c\u1ea3 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/gay-bat-ngo-lon-hlv-olympic-malaysia-lon-tieng-doa-ca-han-quoc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ngo\u00e0i mong \u0111\u1ee3i, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Malaysia \u0111ang v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Chi\u1ec1u qua (15/8), Olympic Malaysia \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn khi th\u1eafng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Kyrgyzstan 3-1. Hi\u1ec7n sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Malaysia t\u1ea1m x\u1ebfp nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng sau H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c do k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i Kyrgyzstan, HLV Ong Kim Swee \u0111ang v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 tin khi cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn, HLV Olympic Malaysia l\u1edbn ti\u1ebfng d\u1ecda c\u1ea3 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"G\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn, HLV Olympic Malaysia l\u1edbn ti\u1ebfng d\u1ecda c\u1ea3 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/untitled-1534406334930473824037.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Malaysia \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ng\u00f4i sao Son Heung-min, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p Malaysia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Malaysia. H\u1ecd c\u00f2n l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf Asiad. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ebf m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi h\u1ecd. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 20 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0u k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Malaysia s\u1ebd g\u00e2y ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. Son Heung-min \u01b0? Trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n 1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc, 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Safawi Rasid, Akhyar Rashid v\u00e0 Syafiq Ahmad l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng khi ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Kyrgyzstan. Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y, Safawi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m: \"T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n \u0111ang gi\u00fap Malaysia t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kho\u1ea3ng v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, HLV Ong Kim Swee t\u1eebng r\u1ea5t bi quan v\u00e0 c\u00f2n tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i r\u00fat lui kh\u1ecfi Asiad do s\u1ee3 kh\u00f4ng gom \u0111\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean U23 Malaysia t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. C\u00f2n nh\u1edb h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 (gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1eadp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n), U23 Malaysia c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ong Kim Swee l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-nepal-la-doi-bong-3-te-tai-asiad-168-194611.html\">Olympic Nepal l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u201c3 t\u1ec7\u201d t\u1ea1i ASIAD</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-nepal-thua-nhan-suc-manh-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194610.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nepal th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/cu-vung-tin-olympic-viet-nam-thua-suc-ha-guc-olympic-nepal-472-194608.html\">C\u1ee9 v\u1eefng tin, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eeba s\u1ee9c h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Olympic Nepal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018-372-194609.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nepal 19h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (Asiad 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-nhat-ban-vs-u23-pakistan-asiad-2018-372-194605.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs U23 Pakistan 16h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (Asiad 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-thai-lan-vs-u23-bangladesh-asiad-2018-372-194604.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Th\u00e1i Lan vs U23 Bangladesh 16h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (Asiad 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-cu-tro-ly-do-tham-han-quoc-168-194601.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1eed tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd do th\u00e1m H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng H\u1ee3p (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2433","checkdouble":"194613"},{"date":"15:46 16/08","title":"B\u00e1o Trung Qu\u1ed1c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/bao-trung-quoc-tin-tuong-olympic-viet-nam-se-xep-tren-nhat-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.\r\n\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018-372-194609.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018-372-194609.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nepal 19h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (Asiad 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nepal: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal b\u1ea3ng B m\u00f4n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D, ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Pakistan sau c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y gi\u00fap\u00a0th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang t\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 b\u1ea3ng D nh\u1edd h\u01a1n Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5.</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n trong n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean c\u1ea1nh tranh cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u1ed9i n\u00e0o gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ebd tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng E, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Trung Qu\u1ed1c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Trung Qu\u1ed1c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Nepal-Co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Trung Qu\u1ed1c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do \u0111\u00f3, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 19/8 t\u1edbi s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D. \u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c n\u00e0y, t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Ifeng \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Sau khi th\u1eafng Pakistan, Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n g\u1eb7p Nepal v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Do Nepal b\u1ecb coi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng xem nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eb1m ch\u1eafc trong tay Vi\u1ec7t Nam. C\u00f2n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i, n\u00ean Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u1ec9nh b\u1ea3ng\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng quan \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean, t\u1edd Sina c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u1ebfm ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00e0y nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201c\u1ede gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018, Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u00e1 qu\u00e2n. H\u1ecd gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean b\u1ed9 khung \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn Asiad, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 sung ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i. D\u00f9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Vi\u1ec7t Nam, nh\u01b0ng ai c\u0169ng hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh. Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u1ea7n ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng Nepal 1-0\u201d. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai, \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t cu\u1ed1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo mong ch\u1edd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-194598.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/2/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-194598.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5</span><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. V\u00e0 ai s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh d\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3?</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/cu-vung-tin-olympic-viet-nam-thua-suc-ha-guc-olympic-nepal-472-194608.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/cu-vung-tin-olympic-viet-nam-thua-suc-ha-guc-olympic-nepal.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/cu-vung-tin-olympic-viet-nam-thua-suc-ha-guc-olympic-nepal-472-194608.html\">C\u1ee9 v\u1eefng tin, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eeba s\u1ee9c h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Olympic Nepal</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 tin tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Nepal l\u00fac 19h h\u00f4m nay. Nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam \u00c1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 r\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ef1ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang-168-194581.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang-168-194581.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal (19h ng\u00e0y 16/8): Duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nG\u1eb7p Nepal \u2013 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, kinh nghi\u1ec7m, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 s\u1edbm v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-thang-nhe-nepal-thoi-co-vang-cho-olympic-viet-nam-168-194550.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/nhat-ban-thang-nhe-nepal-thoi-co-vang-cho-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-thang-nhe-nepal-thoi-co-vang-cho-olympic-viet-nam-168-194550.html\">Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 Nepal: Th\u1eddi c\u01a1 v\u00e0ng cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 Nepal \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng. Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u00f2n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2432","checkdouble":"194614"},{"date":"16:24 16/08","title":"Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/tro-ly-hlv-park-hang-seo-canh-bao-olympic-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-nepal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i 16/8, d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nepal b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018-372-194609.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018-372-194609.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nepal 19h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (Asiad 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nepal: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal b\u1ea3ng B m\u00f4n...</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Pakistan sau c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/Bao-Pakistan-noi-gi-ve-tran-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Pakistan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap h\u1ecd t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D v\u1edbi hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao l\u00e0 Nepal. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Lee Young-jin cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng Nepal \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0. Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i, nh\u01b0ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Nepal t\u1ecf ra v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc. Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal\u201d, \u00f4ng Lee n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u1edd\u00a0Yonhap News\u00a0c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Nepal l\u00e0 h\u1ea1ng 161 tr\u00ean BXH FIFA, trong khi c\u1ee7a Pakistan l\u00e0 201 c\u00f2n Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 102 n\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p coi th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Nepal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 6-3-1. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1 b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Gyotoku s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \"\u0111\u1ed5 b\u00ea t\u00f4ng\" tr\u01b0\u1edbc Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1edfi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111ang th\u1eafng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eadm tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc M\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-nepal-thua-nhan-suc-manh-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194610.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/truyen-thong-nepal-thua-nhan-suc-manh-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-nepal-thua-nhan-suc-manh-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194610.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nepal th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Nepal v\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c gia Nam \u00c1 Nepal cho r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-194598.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/2/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-194598.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5</span><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. V\u00e0 ai s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh d\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3?</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang-168-194581.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang-168-194581.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal (19h ng\u00e0y 16/8): Duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nG\u1eb7p Nepal \u2013 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, kinh nghi\u1ec7m, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 s\u1edbm v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</span></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2431","checkdouble":"194615"},{"date":"16:46 16/08","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do Yerry Mina kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi Man United","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/day-ly-do-yerry-mina-khong-toi-man-united.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Everton v\u1eeba h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 l\u00ed do v\u00ec sao h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park thay v\u00ec Man United.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yerry Mina l\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t gia nh\u1eadp CLB Everton \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean 30 tri\u1ec7u euro. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, CLB Barca ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 11,8 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Mina t\u1eeb Palmeiras.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do Yerry Mina kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi Man United h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do Yerry Mina kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi Man United h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/Day!-Ly-do-Yerry-Mina-khong-toi-Man-United-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Yerry Mina v\u00e0 Andre Gomes l\u00e0 hai ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Everton</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p t\u1ed1t, Mina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.&nbsp;Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Goodison Park, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB M.U theo \u0111u\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh, Everton th\u1eafng trong v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u00ec ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed m\u00f4i gi\u1edbi cho Jair, ng\u01b0\u1eddi &nbsp;\u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Mina c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ch\u00fa c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Man United. Tuy nhi\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Everton, Marcel Brands&nbsp;\u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">GI\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do Yerry Mina kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi Man United, v\u1ecb n\u00e0y cho r\u1eb1ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Everton: &ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed m\u00f4i gi\u1edbi \u1edf m\u1ee9c b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u1ecfi mua v\u00e0 Barca \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd chi cho 1 v\u1ee5 mua s\u1eafm. Barcelona c\u0169ng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Man United nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua mua Mina.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, Mina \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t ki\u00ean \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi t\u00f4i: &lsquo;T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Everton&rsquo;. T\u00f4i h\u01a1i lo l\u1eafng v\u00ec s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a Man United nh\u01b0ng v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng k\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mina v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t l\u00ed do gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch vi\u1ec7c Mina t\u1edbi Everton l\u00e0 v\u00ec anh mu\u1ed1n ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n thay v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh cho su\u1ea5t ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Old Trafford. Ngo\u00e0i ra vi\u1ec7c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea7n ch\u1eeb gi\u1eefa quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua trung v\u1ec7 Colombia v\u00e0 ch\u1edd Leicester nh\u1ea3 Harry Maguire c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 di\u1ec5n ra nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-don-tin-vui-tu-hang-cong-truoc-tran-gap-brighton-172-194551.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/4/mu-don-tin-vui-tu-hang-cong-truoc-tran-gap-brighton.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-don-tin-vui-tu-hang-cong-truoc-tran-gap-brighton-172-194551.html\">MU \u0111\u00f3n tin vui t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Brighton</span><br>\r\nHLV Jose Mourinho \u00fap m\u1edf v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Jesse Lingard v\u00e0 Romelu Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brighton cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-bao-tin-buon-cho-chelsea-172-194549.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/zaha-bao-tin-buon-cho-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-bao-tin-buon-cho-chelsea-172-194549.html\">H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i MU b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Chelsea</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Wilfried Zaha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u ch\u1ea5m h\u1ebft cho nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n xung quanh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Crystal Palace.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zizou-da-san-sang-thay-jose-mourinho-o-mu-172-194539.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/zizou-da-san-sang-thay-jose-mourinho-o-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zizou-da-san-sang-thay-jose-mourinho-o-mu-172-194539.html\">Zizou \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thay Jose Mourinho \u1edf M.U</span><br>\r\nT\u1edd b\u00e1o danh ti\u1ebfng LEquipe (Ph\u00e1p) v\u1eeba loan tin r\u1eb1ng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Zinedine Zidane mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Premier League v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng m\u00e0 Mourinho...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2430","checkdouble":"194617"},{"date":"17:09 16/08","title":"B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng FIFA th\u00e1ng 8/2018: Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 bao nhi\u00eau?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/29/bang-xep-hang-fifa-thang-82018-viet-nam-dung-thu-bao-nhieu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u0110B\u0110 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi FIFA v\u1eeba c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng FIFA th\u00e1ng 8/2018 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn \u1edf nh\u00f3m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u.</h2><div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018-372-194609.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018-372-194609.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nepal 19h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (Asiad 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nepal: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal b\u1ea3ng B m\u00f4n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, nh\u00e0 t\u00e2n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p t\u0103ng 6 h\u1ea1ng, v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng FIFA th\u00e1ng 8/2018 v\u1edbi 1726 \u0111i\u1ec3m, b\u1ecf xa nh\u00e0 c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1edbi 14 b\u1eadc.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p, nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup v\u1eeba qua c\u0169ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean BXH FIFA. \u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Croatia t\u0103ng 16 b\u1eadc \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 4 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1edbi 1643 \u0111i\u1ec3m, ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp sau hai \u0110T B\u1ec9 (1723 \u0111i\u1ec3m) v\u00e0 Brazil (1657 \u0111i\u1ec3m).<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng FIFA th\u00e1ng 82018 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 bao nhi\u00eau h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng FIFA th\u00e1ng 82018 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 bao nhi\u00eau h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/29/bxh-fifa-thang-52018-dt-viet-nam-tiep-tuc-thang-hang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean h\u1ea1ng 102 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng FIFA th\u00e1ng 8/2018\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ee9ng sau Croatia l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 Uruguay (t\u0103ng 9 b\u1eadc), Anh (t\u0103ng 6 b\u1eadc), B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (gi\u00e0m 3 b\u1eadc), Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 (gi\u1ea3m 2 b\u1eadc), T\u00e2y Ban Nha (t\u0103ng 1 b\u1eadc). \u0110an M\u1ea1ch l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng trong t\u1ed1p 10 v\u1edbi 1580 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u00f3 th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i World Cup gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean BXH FIFA th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1eeba qua l\u1ea1i ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i nh\u1eadn c\u00e1c th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i \u0110\u1ee9c, Argentina c\u0169ng t\u1ee5t 6 b\u1eadc xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng 11 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Chile t\u1ee5t 3 b\u1eadc xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng 12 hay Ba Lan t\u1ee5t nh\u1eefng 10 b\u1eadc xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng 18. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ef1u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup Italia th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n v\u1edbi th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng 21, t\u1ee5t 2 b\u1eadc so v\u1edbi th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng FIFA th\u00e1ng 8/2018 c\u0169ng ghi nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 World Cup \u0110T Nga. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y t\u0103ng 21 b\u1eadc \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 49. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Ai C\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah v\u1eeba l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n r\u01a1i \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t (77 \u0111i\u1ec3m), v\u1eeba l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ecb t\u1ee5t h\u1ea1ng kinh kh\u1ee7ng nh\u1ea5t (20 b\u1eadc, xu\u1ed1ng th\u1ee9 65).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1, \u0110T Iran v\u1edbi 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. H\u1ecd \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 32 v\u1edbi 1471 \u0111i\u1ec3m, t\u0103ng 5 b\u1eadc so v\u1edbi th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc. \u0110\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai l\u00e0 \u00dac v\u1edbi 1431 \u0111i\u1ec3m, h\u1ea1ng 43 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u1ea1ng 55 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 102 tr\u00ean BXH, ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 Philippines\u00a0(h\u1ea1ng 115), Th\u00e1i Lan (h\u1ea1ng 122), Myanmar (138). Brunei l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u00f3 th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 v\u1edbi h\u1ea1ng 195 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tro-ly-hlv-park-hang-seo-canh-bao-olympic-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-nepal-168-194615.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/tro-ly-hlv-park-hang-seo-canh-bao-olympic-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-nepal.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tro-ly-hlv-park-hang-seo-canh-bao-olympic-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-nepal-168-194615.html\">Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i 16/8, d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nepal b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-trung-quoc-tin-tuong-olympic-viet-nam-se-xep-tren-nhat-ban-168-194614.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/bao-trung-quoc-tin-tuong-olympic-viet-nam-se-xep-tren-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-trung-quoc-tin-tuong-olympic-viet-nam-se-xep-tren-nhat-ban-168-194614.html\">B\u00e1o Trung Qu\u1ed1c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2429","checkdouble":"194618"},{"date":"09:54 16/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Qatar vs U23 Uzbekistan 19h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (ASIAD 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/nhan-dinh-u23-qatar-vs-u23-uzbekistan-19h00-ngay-168-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 Qatar vs U23 Uzbekistan l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (V\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asian 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Qatar vs U23 Uzbekistan 19h00 ng\u00e0y 168 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Qatar vs U23 Uzbekistan 19h00 ng\u00e0y 168 ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Qatar_-_Uzbekistan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Qatar vs U23 Uzbekistan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span>U23 Qatar vs U23 Uzbekistan: 0-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nQatar c\u00f9ng Uzbekistan \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao cho t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng B m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018 d\u00e0nh cho 2 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng (\u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m 4/6 th\u1ee9 3 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t). Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, Qatar \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 vu\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u00e1i Lan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMu\u1ed1n n\u00edu k\u00e9o hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp Qatar c\u1ea7n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uzbekistan \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng Bangladesh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 di\u1ec5n ra h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m, U23 Qatar t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i U23 Uzbekistan 1-0 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Song cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, trong khi U23 Qatar b\u1ecb U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nU23 Uzbekistan \u0111ang kh\u00e1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i tinh th\u1ea7n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bangladesh v\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n th\u00eam 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u1eefa l\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111ang \u0111i theo chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho h\u1ecd.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/094822-bxh-bangb-asiad-2018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2428","checkdouble":"194593"},{"date":"10:11 16/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Atalanta vs Hapoel Haifa 01h00 ng\u00e0y 17/8 (Europa League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/nhan-dinh-atalanta-vs-hapoel-haifa-01h00-ngay-178-europa-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Atalanta vs Hapoel Haifa l\u00fac 01h00 ng\u00e0y 17/8 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Europa League/c\u00fap C2 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Atalanta vs Hapoel Haifa 01h00 ng\u00e0y 178 Europa League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Atalanta vs Hapoel Haifa 01h00 ng\u00e0y 178 Europa League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Atalanta-vs-Hapoel-Haifa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Atalanta vs Hapoel Haifa</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span> </span>Atalanta vs Hapoel Haifa: 2-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a 2001/02, Hapoel Haifa l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. \u1ede v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 3 Europa League, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Israel c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Atalanta \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Serie A n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-4 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00eam nay, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Gian Piero Gasperini \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c t\u1ea1o ra 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng n\u1eefa. Nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u Atalanta c\u00f3 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. N\u00ean nh\u1edb, ch\u1ec9 \u00edt ng\u00e0y sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Atalanta s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Serie A 2018-19 v\u1edbi Frosinone. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3, HLV Gasperini c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Hapoel Haifa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Hapoel Haifa, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady, trong chuy\u1ebfn vi\u1ebfng th\u0103m Italia \u0111\u00eam nay, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u1ea3 d\u0129 nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng v\u1edbi 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 n\u00e0y, Atalanta v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 h\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c, trong khi Hapoel Haifa s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n thua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- \u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, Atalanta \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Hapoel Haifa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n+ Atalanta (3-5-2): Berisha - Palomino, Toloi, Masiello - Hateboer, Freuler, Pasalic, De Roon, Gosens - Cornelius, Zapata.<br>\r\n+ Hapoel Haifa (4-3-3): Setkus - Malul, Kapiloto, Tamas, Dilmoni - Sjostedt, Vermouth, Plakushchenko - Buzaglo, Ginsari, Papazoglou.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2427","checkdouble":"194594"},{"date":"10:18 16/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Basel vs Vitesse 1h00 ng\u00e0y 17/8 (Europa League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/nhan-dinh-basel-vs-vitesse-1h00-ngay-178-europa-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. V\u00e0 ai s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh d\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3?</h2><h2>Khi xoay tua \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1 xong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Pakistan c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y hai h\u00f4m, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u qua 15/8. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 n\u00f3i: \u201c\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y mai ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn\u00a0U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 v\u00e0i s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Pakistan.\u00a0T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng lo l\u1eafng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111a s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nhau t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1\u201d.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Nepal-Co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u00a0vs Olympic Nepal</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c xoay tua \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh m\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f2n gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y Park t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 59 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y tr\u00e1nh b\u1ecb th\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9ng khi b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eaft b\u00e0i n\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n h\u1ebft, vi\u1ec7c th\u1ea7y Park trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh trong to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, khi m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ai ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m trong m\u1eaft ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1eb7p Nepal, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo tung \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 2 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang c\u00f3 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00fac n\u00e0y, HLV Park c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Ai s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t trong h\u00e0ng trung v\u1ec7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec l\u00fd do \u0111\u00f3, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi V\u0103n L\u1ee3i. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 r\u1ea5t x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t C\u1ea3ng. Ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t, anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xuan Manh choi cuc hay trong tran tu ket voi U23 Iraq\" title=\"Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c hay trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi U23 Iraq\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/31/Hau-ve-Xuan-Manh-mong-mau-co-tien-thuong-de-tra-no-cho-bo-me-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c hay t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n v\u1ec1 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eeba qua. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i V-League n\u0103m nay, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00ean c\u00f4ng, v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7. \u00a0Do \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111ang d\u00e0nh cho \u0110\u1ee9c Huy v\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 Quang H\u1ea3i l\u00e0 hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1n xuy\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Song r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i quen thu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea9y V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm thay cho Anh \u0110\u1ee9c. L\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c anh v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Wibawa Mukti, T\u00e2y Java (Indonesia) v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn, m\u1eddi qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 quan t\u00e2m theo d\u00f5i./.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal:</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n L\u1ee3i, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Nepal: Kiran Chemjong, Tamang, Chaudhary, Shrestha, Budhathoki, Rohit Chand, Gurung, Bista, Magar, Bharat Khawas, Magar.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang-168-194581.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang-168-194581.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal (19h ng\u00e0y 16/8): Duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nG\u1eb7p Nepal \u2013 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, kinh nghi\u1ec7m, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 s\u1edbm v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-olympic-viet-nam-lai-vao-chung-ket-duoc-chu-sao-khong-168-194536.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-olympic-viet-nam-lai-vao-chung-ket-duoc-chu-sao-khong-168-194536.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft Asiad 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9, sao kh\u00f4ng?</span><br>\r\nTrong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 tin th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u1ee7...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-thang-nhe-nepal-thoi-co-vang-cho-olympic-viet-nam-168-194550.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/nhat-ban-thang-nhe-nepal-thoi-co-vang-cho-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-thang-nhe-nepal-thoi-co-vang-cho-olympic-viet-nam-168-194550.html\">Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 Nepal: Th\u1eddi c\u01a1 v\u00e0ng cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 Nepal \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng. Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u00f2n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2426","checkdouble":"194595"},{"date":"10:31 16/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Feyenoord vs Trencin 1h30 ng\u00e0y 17/8 (Europa League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/nhan-dinh-feyenoord-vs-trencin-1h30-ngay-178-europa-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Feyenoord vs Trencin l\u00fac 1h30 ng\u00e0y 17/8 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Europa League/c\u00fap C2 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Feyenoord vs Trencin 1h30 ng\u00e0y 178 Europa League 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Feyenoord vs Trencin 1h30 ng\u00e0y 178 Europa League 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Nhan-dinh-bong-da-feyenoord-vs-trencin-01h30-ngay-1708-noi-nhuc-kho-rua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Feyenoord vs Trencin</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span> </span>Feyenoord vs Trencin: 2-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Trencin \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 3 UEFA Europa League, khi th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan Feyenoord t\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, d\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a hoa Tuylip, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Slovakia nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd c\u1ea7m ch\u1eafc t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh <br>\r\n<br>\r\nFeyenoord \u0111ang h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n sau khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua PSV Eindhoven \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap H\u00e0 Lan. Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u sau \u0111\u00f3 g\u1eb7p Trencin l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c. Feyenoord thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn ra l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1eeda tr\u00ean. Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n,\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng H\u00e0 Lan kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u00eam b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i n\u00e0o \u1edf tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ed3m hatrick c\u1ee7a Mance v\u00e0 1 b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Azango \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Trencin nh\u1ea5n ch\u00ecm Feyenoord. Tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7t ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stadion Feijenoord t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ed1 2 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 n\u00e0y Feyenoord s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 ki\u1ebfm v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng danh d\u1ef1 m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrencin v\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Zilina 3-2 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG\u00a0Slovakia 2018/19. Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y c\u00f2n gi\u00fap h\u1ecd n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i m\u1ea1ch to\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 4 tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng (16 b\u00e0n th\u00e1ng).\u00a0 Xa h\u01a1n qua 10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Trencin m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 s\u1ea9y ch\u00e2n \u0111\u00fang 1 l\u1ea7n duy nh\u1ea5t. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, gi\u1ea5c m\u1ed9ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u1ee7a Feyenoord g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 tan v\u1ee1 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2425","checkdouble":"194597"},{"date":"11:05 16/08","title":"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/2/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. V\u00e0 ai s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh d\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3?</h2><h2>Khi xoay tua \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1 xong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Pakistan c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y hai h\u00f4m, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u qua 15/8. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 n\u00f3i: \u201c\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y mai ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn\u00a0U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 v\u00e0i s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Pakistan.\u00a0T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng lo l\u1eafng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111a s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nhau t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1\u201d.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Nepal-Co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u00a0vs Olympic Nepal</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c xoay tua \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh m\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f2n gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y Park t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 59 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y tr\u00e1nh b\u1ecb th\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9ng khi b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eaft b\u00e0i n\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n h\u1ebft, vi\u1ec7c th\u1ea7y Park trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh trong to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, khi m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ai ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m trong m\u1eaft ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1eb7p Nepal, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo tung \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 2 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang c\u00f3 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00fac n\u00e0y, HLV Park c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Ai s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t trong h\u00e0ng trung v\u1ec7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec l\u00fd do \u0111\u00f3, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi V\u0103n L\u1ee3i. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 r\u1ea5t x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t C\u1ea3ng. Ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t, anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xuan Manh choi cuc hay trong tran tu ket voi U23 Iraq\" title=\"Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c hay trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi U23 Iraq\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/31/Hau-ve-Xuan-Manh-mong-mau-co-tien-thuong-de-tra-no-cho-bo-me-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c hay t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n v\u1ec1 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eeba qua. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i V-League n\u0103m nay, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00ean c\u00f4ng, v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7. \u00a0Do \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111ang d\u00e0nh cho \u0110\u1ee9c Huy v\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 Quang H\u1ea3i l\u00e0 hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1n xuy\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Song r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i quen thu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea9y V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm thay cho Anh \u0110\u1ee9c. L\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c anh v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Wibawa Mukti, T\u00e2y Java (Indonesia) v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn, m\u1eddi qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 quan t\u00e2m theo d\u00f5i./.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal:</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n L\u1ee3i, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Nepal: Kiran Chemjong, Tamang, Chaudhary, Shrestha, Budhathoki, Rohit Chand, Gurung, Bista, Magar, Bharat Khawas, Magar.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang-168-194581.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang-168-194581.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal (19h ng\u00e0y 16/8): Duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nG\u1eb7p Nepal \u2013 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, kinh nghi\u1ec7m, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 s\u1edbm v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-olympic-viet-nam-lai-vao-chung-ket-duoc-chu-sao-khong-168-194536.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-olympic-viet-nam-lai-vao-chung-ket-duoc-chu-sao-khong-168-194536.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft Asiad 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9, sao kh\u00f4ng?</span><br>\r\nTrong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 tin th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u1ee7...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-thang-nhe-nepal-thoi-co-vang-cho-olympic-viet-nam-168-194550.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/nhat-ban-thang-nhe-nepal-thoi-co-vang-cho-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-thang-nhe-nepal-thoi-co-vang-cho-olympic-viet-nam-168-194550.html\">Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 Nepal: Th\u1eddi c\u01a1 v\u00e0ng cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 Nepal \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng. Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u00f2n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2424","checkdouble":"194598"}]}